This paper is focused on malware detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data analytics and machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of statistical and kernel-based SVM classifiers also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
